}} || <center>'''5'''\u20131</center> || <center>5\u20131</center> || Friendly\n|-\n| <center>19.</center> ||12 November 2011 || [[Cardiff City Stadium]], Cardiff, Wales || {{fb|Norway}} || <center>'''2'''\u20130</center> || <center>4\u20131</center> || Friendly\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n{{col-start}}\n{{col-break|width=20%}}\n'''Great Britain statistics'''\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\" style=\"text-align:center\"\n|-\n!colspan=\"3\"|[[Great Britain Olympic football team|Great Britain Olympic team]]\n|-\n!Year!!{{Tooltip|Apps|Appearances}}!!Goals\n|-\n|2012||5||1\n|-\n!Total||5||1\n|}\n<ref>{{cite web|title=Craig Bellamy&nbsp;\u2013 2012/13 statistics|url=http://www.espnfc.com/player/_/id/8952/craig-bellamy?cc=4716|publisher=ESPN FC|accessdate=28 May 2014|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140529052220/http://www.espnfc.com/player/_/id/8952/craig-bellamy?cc=4716|archive-date=29 May 2014|url-status=live}}</ref>\n\n{{col-break|width=80%}}\n'''Great Britain international goals'''\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Goal !! width=120|Date !! width=280|Venue !! width=120|Opponent !! Score !! Result !! Competition\n|-\n| 1.<ref name=gb1/> || 26 July 2012 || [[Old Trafford]], [[Manchester]], England || {{fb|Senegal}} || <center>'''1'''\u20130</center> || <center>1\u20131</center> || [[Football at the 2012 Summer Olympics&nbsp;\u2013 Men's tournament|2012 Summer Olympics]]\n|}\n{{col-end}}\n\n== Honours ==\n\n=== Club ===\n;[[Celtic F.C.|Celtic]]\n*[[Scottish Cup]]: [[2005 Scottish Cup Final|2004\u201305]]\n\n;[[Liverpool F.C.|Liverpool]]\n*[[Football League Cup|League Cup]]: [[2012 Football League Cup Final|2011\u201312]]\n*[[FA Community Shield]]: [[2006 FA Community Shield|2006]]\n\n;[[Cardiff City F.C.|Cardiff City]]\n*[[Football League Championship]]: [[2012-13 Football League Championship|2012\u201313]]\n\n=== Individual ===\n*Welsh Player of the Year Award: 2007\n*[[PFA Young Player of the Year|PFA Young Player of the Year Award]]: 2001\u201302\n*[[Blackburn Rovers F.C.#Play